    "For less than 365 days of data, values are extrapolated to a full year with corresponding inaccuracy depending on the captured period.": "当数据少于365天时，数值会外推到全年，误差取决于已覆盖的时间段。",
    "Kilometers are captured only while a vehicle is plugged in. If plugged in rarely, kilometers can be missing.": "只有在车辆接入时才会记录公里数。如果接入频率较低，公里数可能会缺失。",
    "Uses the average yield of the best 30 days per year. This can help identify possible degradation, but must be interpreted in context. Individual years are not conclusive on their own.": "使用每年最佳30天的平均发电量。这有助于识别可能的衰减，但必须结合上下文解读。单独某一年并不能得出结论。",
    "Uses the average yield of the best 5 days per month. This can help identify possible degradation, but must be interpreted in context. Individual months are not conclusive on their own.": "使用每月最佳5天的平均发电量。这有助于识别可能的衰减，但必须结合上下文解读。单独某个月并不能得出结论。",
    "Values are approximate. External charging is not included and captured kilometers depend on how often a vehicle is plugged in.": "这些值为近似值。不包含外部充电，记录到的公里数取决于车辆接入的频率。",
    "Values are rough estimates based on averages. External charging sessions are not included.": "这些值是基于平均值的粗略估算。不包含外部充电会话。",
